purpose: To serve as a starting point for developers to create AI agents that can integrate with Collab.Land ecosystems.
principle: Built using TypeScript with a focus on modularity and extensibility, allowing developers to easily customize and expand functionality.
reusability: Designed as a modular and extensible framework, enabling developers to build on top of its core functionalities and integrate with other systems.
limitations: Primarily in alpha stage, so may lack comprehensive documentation and stability. Limited to use cases supported by Collab.Land.
name: AI-Agent-Starter-Kit
highlight: Provides a foundational framework for building AI agents with Collab.Land integration.
